name: Swedish Gymnastics Association 30 Year Plaque
obverse: Bust of a male gymnast facing right inside a circle with a blue background. Inscription in 9 lines with engraved name at the bottom.
obverse_inscriptions: SVENSKA GYMNASTIKFÖRBUNDETS PLAKETT FÖR 30-ÅRIGT INTRESSERAT DELTAGANDE I GYNASTIKÖVNINGAR TILL
description: This medal was made by the Swedish Gymnastics Associations to celebrate 30 years of interest in gymnastics.
